node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jo Lindner in Thailand. May be an image of 1 person, beard and indoor.

node.text: Current situation. At 101kg. Looks skinny tho because my muscles are all empty. No workouts. Just now slowly getting back to the gym. Gyno feels like it’s quite good healed now. Biceps feels like need another 4-6 weeks to be back to feeling „normal“  ty for all your support 🙏🏾🙏🏾
Thailand outdoor gym was good @youngla perfect jogger is rly cool and crazy stretchy material like a Pyjama xD . / Werbung - Code : JO
